data.description: This townhome in Hunters Ridge is the easiest way to live in Louisville! The 3BR/3BA unit has spacious living areas on all three levels. New paint, flooring and updates throughout. The living room has a gas fireplace and formal dining area. Updated kitchen with stainless appliances and lots of storage in cabinets and pantry.  Second floor boasts two roomy bedrooms with vaulted ceilings. One has a jack and jill 3/4 bath. One has an attached full bath and a peaceful south facing bedroom balcony with tree cover.  A fully finished basement allows for another living space and bedroom, plus laundry and utilities.  South facing deck off the  kitchen has lovely ambiance. Central Air for your comfort all year long! Low HOA in this well maintained community.  Spacious lawn and green spaces make having pets easy. Walkable to Downtown Louisville or 3 minute drive.  Abundant trails and parks accessible, and multiple BVSD schools in proximity.
